com.cc.inputs.driver

Class Driver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cc.inputs.driver.Driver
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AirplaneController, AttackThree, XBoxController

    public abstract class Driver
extends Object
    Driver provides an interface for the three controller types to implement. It allows the three controller types to be called driver and provides the ability to have a singleton.
